      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sebring%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Sebring’s train station, built in 1924 by the Seaboard Air Line, is listed on the National Register of Historic Places.",
